nl: Lütfen Notları "Current series on No slogan" olarak belirten sıraların sayısını, beş sonuçta sınırlı olarak, aşağıdaki sırada elde edilen sayıya göre düzenlenen Notlar ile gruplandırın.
sql:
SELECT `Notes`, COUNT(*) AS `Count`
FROM `table_1_1000181_1`
WHERE `Notes` = 'No slogan on current series'
GROUP BY `Notes`
ORDER BY `Count` DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT col5, COUNT(*) AS `Count`
FROM `table_1_1000181_1`
WHERE col5 LIKE '%No slogan%'
GROUP BY col5
ORDER BY `Count` DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: Flot kayıtlarından, Her Üreticiden kaç giriş mevcut olduğunu listeleyin, ancak sadece birden fazla giriş yapan üreticileri içerelim, sonuçları en küçükten en büyüke kadar giriş sayısına göre sıralayın ve beş üreticine kadar geri gönderin.
sql:
SELECT `Manufacturer`, COUNT(*)
FROM `table_1_10007452_3`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY `Manufacturer`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY 2
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT col1, COUNT(*)
FROM `table_1_10007452_3`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY col1
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY 2
LIMIT 5;

nl: Raptors tüm zaman listesinde temsil edilen her milliyet için, kaç oyuncu var ve bu milliyetten herhangi bir oyuncu Toronto'da ilk başladığı yıl nedir?
sql:
SELECT
  `Nationality` AS `Nation`,
  COUNT(*) AS `Num Players`,
  MIN(CAST(substr(`Years in Toronto`, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) AS `Earliest Start Year`,
  CASE
    WHEN MIN(CAST(substr(`Years in Toronto`, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 2000 THEN '1990s'
    WHEN MIN(CAST(substr(`Years in Toronto`, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 2010 THEN '2000s'
    ELSE '2010s+'
  END AS `Era`,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT `School/Club Team`) AS `Feeding Schools/Clubs`,
  SUM(CASE WHEN `Years in Toronto` LIKE '%,%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `MultiStintCount`
FROM `table_1_10015132_1`
GROUP BY `Nationality`
ORDER BY `Era`, `Nation`;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col2 AS `Nation`,
  COUNT(*) AS `Num Players`,
  MIN(CAST(substr(col4, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) AS `Earliest Start Year`,
  CASE
    WHEN MIN(CAST(substr(col4, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 2000 THEN '1990s'
    WHEN MIN(CAST(substr(col4, 1, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 2010 THEN '2000s'
    ELSE '2010s+'
  END AS `Era`,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT col5) AS `Feeding Schools/Clubs`,
  SUM(CASE WHEN col4 LIKE '%,%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `MultiStintCount`
FROM `table_1_10015132_1`
GROUP BY col2
ORDER BY `Era`, `Nation`;

nl: Her ayrı pozisyonu, bu pozisyonda bulunan oyuncuların sayısı ile listeleyin ve sayıya göre sadece en üst beş pozisyonu gösterin.
sql:

FROM `table_1_10015132_21`

GROUP BY `Position`

db_sql:

FROM `table_1_10015132_21`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY col3
ORDER BY `cnt` DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: Raptors tüm zaman listesinin girişlerini, Toronto'daki isim, gömlek numarasını, milliyetini, konumunu, yıllarını ve okul / kulüp takımını göstererek, gömlek numarasıyla sıralama yaparken ilk beş farklı oyuncunun listesini yukarı doğru sıralayın; Toronto'daki Yıllar 'gelen' ve Aktif olmayan başka bir şekilde içerdiğinde aktif durumunu ekleyin ve listesdeki oyuncuların toplam sayısını ekleyin.
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
  `Player`,
  `No.`,
  `Nationality`,
  `Position`,
  `Years in Toronto`,
  `School/Club Team`,
  CASE
    WHEN `Years in Toronto` LIKE '%present%' THEN 'Active'
    ELSE 'Inactive'
  END AS `Status`,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM `table_1_10015132_7`) AS `TotalPlayers`
FROM `table_1_10015132_7`
WHERE 1=1 AND 1=1 OR 1=1
ORDER BY `No.` ASC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
  col0,
  col1,
  col2,
  col3,
  col4,
  col5,
  CASE
    WHEN col4 LIKE '%present%' THEN 'Active'
    ELSE 'Inactive'
  END AS `Status`,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM `table_1_10015132_7`) AS `TotalPlayers`
FROM `table_1_10015132_7`
WHERE 1=1 AND 1=1 OR 1=1
ORDER BY col1 ASC
LIMIT 5;

nl: Yüksek barajlar için (Yükseklik >= 150 m) tek bir konsolidasyon raporunu sunarak şunları içerir: (a) sayıları, ortalama yüksekliği ve maksimum zirve uzunluğu ile her kantona ve tür başına dağılımı; (b) isimleri, kantonu, inşa yılı, yüksekliği ve zirve uzunluğu ile en eski beş yüksek baraj; ve (c) isimleri, kantonu, türü, yüksekliği, zirve uzunluğu ve oranı ile en yüksek beş yüksekliğe oranlı baraj.
sql:
WITH tall AS (
  SELECT `Name` AS Name,
         `Canton` AS Canton,
         `Height (meters)` AS Height,
         `Crest length (meters)` AS Crest,
         `Type` AS Type,
         `Year of construction` AS Year,
         `Name of the Lake` AS Lake
  FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
  WHERE `Height (meters)` >= 150
),
by_block AS (
  SELECT 'BY_CANTON_TYPE' AS `Block`,
         Canton AS `Col1`,
         Type AS `Col2`,
         COUNT(*) AS `Col3`,
         AVG(Height) AS `Col4`,
         MAX(Crest) AS `Col5`,
         NULL AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM tall
  GROUP BY Canton, Type
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC, AVG(Height) DESC
),
oldest_tall AS (
  SELECT 'OLDEST_TALL' AS `Block`,
         Name AS `Col1`,
         Canton AS `Col2`,
         Year AS `Col3`,
         Height AS `Col4`,
         Crest AS `Col5`,
         NULL AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM tall
  ORDER BY Year ASC
  LIMIT 5
),
ratio_rank AS (
  SELECT 'HIGHEST_RATIO' AS `Block`,
         Name AS `Col1`,
         Canton AS `Col2`,
         Type AS `Col3`,
         Height AS `Col4`,
         Crest AS `Col5`,
         (Crest * 1.0) / Height AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM tall
  ORDER BY (Crest * 1.0) / Height DESC
  LIMIT 5
)
SELECT * FROM by_block
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM oldest_tall
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM ratio_rank;
db_sql:
WITH tall AS (
  SELECT col0 AS Name,
         col1 AS Canton,
         col2 AS Height,
         col3 AS Crest,
         col4 AS Type,
         col5 AS Year,
         col6 AS Lake
  FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
  WHERE col2 >= 150
),
by_block AS (
  SELECT 'BY_CANTON_TYPE' AS `Block`,
         Canton AS `Col1`,
         Type AS `Col2`,
         COUNT(*) AS `Col3`,
         AVG(Height) AS `Col4`,
         MAX(Crest) AS `Col5`,
         NULL AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
  GROUP BY Canton, Type
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC, AVG(Height) DESC
),
oldest_tall AS (
  SELECT 'OLDEST_TALL' AS `Block`,
         Name AS `Col1`,
         Canton AS `Col2`,
         Year AS `Col3`,
         Height AS `Col4`,
         Crest AS `Col5`,
         NULL AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
  ORDER BY Year ASC
  LIMIT 5
),
ratio_rank AS (
  SELECT 'HIGHEST_RATIO' AS `Block`,
         Name AS `Col1`,
         Canton AS `Col2`,
         Type AS `Col3`,
         Height AS `Col4`,
         Crest AS `Col5`,
         (Crest * 1.0) / Height AS `Col6`,
         NULL AS `Col7`
  FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
  ORDER BY (Crest * 1.0) / Height DESC
  LIMIT 5
)
SELECT * FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM `table_1_10020178_1`
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM `table_1_10020178_1`

nl: LPGA Tour kariyer özetinin verilerine göre, 2007 ve 2012 yılları arasında en çok para kazandığı yıl hangisidir ve o yıl için Yıl ve Kazançlar ($) nedir?
sql:
SELECT
  `Year`,
  `Earnings ($)`
FROM `table_1_10021158_3`
WHERE `Year` BETWEEN 2007 AND 2012
ORDER BY `Earnings ($)` DESC
LIMIT 1;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col0,
  col7
FROM `table_1_10021158_3`
WHERE col0 BETWEEN 2007 AND 2012
ORDER BY col7 DESC
LIMIT 1;

nl: Eğer kazananları milliyetlerine göre gruplarsanız ve kazananların sayısını en yüksekten en düşüke kadar sıralarsanız, hangi milliyet önce gelir ve kaç kazanan vardır?
sql:
SELECT
  `Nationality`, COUNT(*) AS `Count`
FROM `table_1_1004033_1`

GROUP BY `Nationality`
ORDER BY `Count` DESC
LIMIT 1;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col3, COUNT(*) AS `Count`

WHERE 1
GROUP BY col3
ORDER BY `Count` DESC
LIMIT 1;

nl: Her Karargâh için en fazla Bölüm değeri hesaplayın ve Karargâh ve Max Bölüm olarak sunun; Karargâh'a filtreleyin, Karargâh'a karşı maksimum değeri tüm tabloda bulunan en fazla Bölüm değeriyle eşittir; sonuçları Karargâh ile sıralayın.
sql:
SELECT `Headquarters`, MAX(`Chapters`) AS `Max Chapters`
FROM `table_1_10054296_1`
GROUP BY `Headquarters`
HAVING MAX(`Chapters`) = (
  SELECT MAX(`Chapters`)
  FROM `table_1_10054296_1`
)
ORDER BY `Headquarters`;
db_sql:
SELECT col1, MAX(col3) AS `Max Chapters`
FROM `table_1_10054296_1`
GROUP BY col1
HAVING MAX(col3) = (
  SELECT MAX(col3)
  FROM `table_1_10054296_1`
)
ORDER BY col1;
